// Akhri (Input) Function Example
// This example shows how to use akhri to get user input

// First, let's print a brief explanation
qor("Akhri Example - User Input in Soplang")
qor("---------------------------------")

// Using akhri to get the user's name
door magac = akhri("Enter your name: ")

// Display a greeting with the entered name
qor("Hello, " + magac + "!")
qor("Welcome to Soplang programming!")

// Show the type of the input (always a string)
qor("The type of your input is: " + nuuc(magac))

// Example of simple input processing
qor("Your name has several characters.")

// Thank the user
qor("Thank you for trying akhri in Soplang!")
